{"tid":430050,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[10月新番]相睇對象是強硬問題學生","createTime":"2017-10-09T12:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T14:01:11.000Z","uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b48358bf59fbe4288156474358c1583e26a8d41b","tid":430050,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/205124_196cfc137986f4ef5ab0d6b5fb0cb443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F205124_196cfc137986f4ef5ab0d6b5fb0cb443.jpg&h=fad914a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>劇情簡介<del>人渣的本願前傳</del></strong><br />\n<br />\n故事的女主角是學校中的<del>音樂</del>女老師<del>皆川茜</del>菜乃，<del>皆川茜</del>菜乃在學校中深受<del>老師</del>學生們的愛戴，但是卻對自己負責的問題學生久我宗二毫無辦法，某天回家<del>皆川茜</del>菜乃被父母安排相親，相親的對象是高宮宗一郎，而在相親的當天宗一郎各個方面都很優秀，<del>皆川茜</del>菜乃也有所心動，決定要與宗一郎共同度過一晚，當晚第一次感受到身為女人的快感的<del>皆川茜</del>菜乃，一覺醒來發現和自己在一起的其實是自己的學生久我宗二，他打扮成了自己的親哥哥高宮宗一郎和老師相親。<br />\n<br />\n【STAFF】<br />\n<br />\n監督、系列構成・腳本：みうらさぶろう<br />\n<br />\n角色設計、總作畫監督：びんめ<br />\n<br />\n動畫製作:SEVEN<br />\n<br />\n【CAST】<br />\n<br />\n齊川菜乃：本泉莉奈（修正版）、青井美海（無修版）<br />\n<br />\n久我宗二役：白井悠介（修正版）、古河徹人（無修版）<br />\n<br />\n高宮宗一郎：新垣樽助（修正版）、櫻井真人（無修版）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/205636_4084c0f18f3494ee0b8503a00d254e67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F205636_4084c0f18f3494ee0b8503a00d254e67.jpg&h=04fd09d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/205637_4084c0f18f3494ee0b8503a00d254e67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F205637_4084c0f18f3494ee0b8503a00d254e67.jpg&h=ecea9979&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/205637_e23fd39f93d61c91005b4ce85feff19b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt